comments: Simmons (PHI) maintains a legal guarding position as he defends Young (ATL) and does not affect his SQBR.
Horford (PHI) makes incidental contact to the arm of Len (ATL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Bembry (ATL) during the rebound.
Horford (PHI) makes marginal contact with Collins (ATL) off ball in the post that does not affect his ability to defend the pass.
Embiid (PHI) makes brief contact with Collins (ATL) during the rebound.
Collins (ATL) and Simmons (PHI) engage and separate on the legal pick by Collins (ATL).
Young (ATL) makes marginal hand to arm contact with Embiid (PHI) following the rebound.
Reddish (ATL) commits a hop step travel.
Embiid (PHI) releases the pass prior to his right foot landing on the floor.
Reddish (ATL) makes marginal hand to arm contact with Harris (PHI) during his shot attempt.
Simmons (PHI) and Young (ATL) engage and separate off ball.
Young (ATL) initiates marginal contact with Harris (PHI) off ball.
Richardson (PHI) legally contests the shot attempt by hunter (ATL).
Len (ATL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Embiid (PHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Young (ATL) and Richardson (PHI) engage and disengage while rebounding.
Simmons (PHI) makes contact to Collins' (ATL) lower body and dislodges him from his position after he has secured the loose ball.
Embiid (PHI) commits a take foul on Young (ATL).
Horford (PHI) and Collins (ATL) engage and disengage while rebounding.
Collins (ATL) wraps Embiid (PHI) and affects his ability to receive the pass in the post.
Richardson (PHI) makes marginal arm contact with Carter (ATL) prior to the shot attempt.
